OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has promised to change
OL,7,Fpolitics, bring power out of London,
OL,8,Fand undo the legacy of Margaret
OL,9,FThatcher, but what does all that mean
OL,10,Ffor the Midlands?
OL,12,FWe don't know much about Burnham's
OL,13,Fplans; he wasn't elected on the back
OL,14,Fof a manifesto and has promised to
OL,15,Fgive us a detailed look at his cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving policies tomorrow, Tuesday,
OL,17,FJuly 21st.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
