CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FBut his first speech as PM and
OL,7,Fprevious comments can give us some
OL,8,Fidea of his plans and what it means
OL,9,Ffor us.
OL,11,FEnd rough sleeping
OL,13,FAndy Burnham's first pledge as Prime
OL,14,FMinister is to bring an end to rough
OL,15,Fsleeping.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FThe most recent figures show almost
OL,7,F378 people were recorded as sleeping
OL,8,Frough in the West Midlands and 387
OL,9,Fpeople in the East Midlands. That's
OL,10,Faround 16% of all the rough sleepers
OL,11,Fin the country.
OL,13,FWhilst we are still waiting for
OL,14,Fdetails on the plans, the government
OL,15,Fhas hinted there will be more
OL,16,Fresources for councils and the NHS to
OL,17,Fhelp vulnerable people in winter.
OL,19,FIt's also said that 'local leaders'
OL,20,Fwill lead the delivery of the rough
OL,21,Fsleeping projects.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FThis comes as West Midlands Mayor
OL,7,FRichard Parker has told ITV Central
OL,8,Fthat mayors will be getting more money.
OL,10,FIn an interview after Burnham's
OL,11,Fspeech, Richard Parker said that he'll
OL,12,Fbe able to deliver on projects like
OL,13,Fhouse building and ending rough
OL,14,Fsleeping using an increased share of
OL,15,Fthe taxes that are raised in the West
OL,16,FMidlands area.
OL,18,FThis pledge is familiar territory for
OL,19,Fthe new PM; ending rough sleeping was
OL,20,Falso one of his first promises as
OL,21,FMayor of Greater Manchester.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FAlong with the West Midlands Combined
OL,7,FAuthority, they piloted a novel way of
OL,8,Fstopping rough sleeping called
OL,9,F'Housing First'.
OL,11,FThis scheme gave people at risk of
OL,12,Fhomelessness a house as a starting
OL,13,Fpoint to recovery rather than a goal
OL,14,Fto work towards.
OL,16,FThis programme was part of a number of
OL,17,Fmeasures that helped Andy Burnham
OL,18,Fbring rough sleeping down to double
OL,19,Fdigits for the first time since 2013.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
