CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FAlthough after that achievement, rough
OL,7,Fsleeping has risen in Greater
OL,8,FManchester each year since that 2021
OL,9,Flow.
OL,11,FThe jobs at the top
OL,13,FShabana Mahmood, Birmingham Ladywood
OL,14,FMP and the rising star of Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's government, is odds-on to
OL,16,Fbecome Andy Burnham's chancellor.
OL,18,FAndy Burnham has said that changing
OL,19,Fthe Treasury is essential to bringing
OL,20,Fmore wealth to parts of the country
OL,21,Foutside of London and the South East.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FIn his book "Head North", written in
OL,7,F2024 ahead of his reelection as
OL,8,FManchester Mayor, he argues that the
OL,9,FTreasury's system for rating the value
OL,10,Ffor money of infrastructure projects
OL,11,Fdiscriminates against those outside
OL,12,FLondon.
OL,14,FHe says that without a fundamental
OL,15,Fchange in how the treasury operates,
OL,16,Fany projects in places like the
OL,17,FMidlands face an uphill battle to get
OL,18,Fgovernment funding.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FShabana Mahmood will take on the
OL,7,Fresponsibility for making change
OL,8,Fhappen.
OL,10,FOutside of Shabana Mahmood, there is
OL,11,Flikely to be little Midlands
OL,12,Frepresentation in the cabinet.
OL,14,FOnly four of the twenty-five MPs who
OL,15,Fattended Keir Starmer's cabinet
OL,16,Frepresented constituencies in either
OL,17,Fthe West or the East Midlands.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FWith both Pat McFadden, Wolverhampton
OL,7,FSouth, and Liz Kendall, Leicester
OL,8,FWest, rumoured to be on the way out,
OL,9,Fthat number could become even smaller.
OL,11,FThe squeezed Midlands?
OL,13,FAndy Burnham's defining idea is
OL,14,Fdevolution.
OL,16,FTaking power out of the hands of
OL,17,Fpeople in London and Westminster and
OL,18,Fspreading it across the country.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
