PN,34810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FIn his first speech after officially
OL,7,Flaunching his bid to be Labour leader,
OL,8,Fhe said he wanted to "oversee the
OL,9,Fbiggest rebalancing of power our
OL,10,Fcountry has ever seen".
OL,12,FHe has pledged to make a No. 10 in the
OL,13,FNorth, with the goal of supporting the
OL,14,FMidlands and regions across the
OL,15,Fcountry in reforming utilities,
OL,16,Freindustrialising, and regenerating
OL,17,Ftheir local economies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FAll three of these issues are highly
OL,7,Frelevant to the Midlands, which has
OL,8,Fseen manufacturing, the industry that
OL,9,Fonce defined the area, collapse.
OL,11,FBut this plan has left some asking
OL,12,Fwhether the Midlands is about to be
OL,13,Fcaught in a no man's land during the
OL,14,Fpower struggle between the
OL,15,Ftraditionally dominant South and a
OL,16,Fnewly powerful North.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FRichard Parker, Mayor of the West
OL,7,FMidlands, says he's not worried about
OL,8,Fthe Midlands being left behind, "He
OL,9,F(Andy Burnham) understands places like
OL,10,Fthe West Midlands. His focus is on
OL,11,Finvesting in our regions and in our
OL,12,Fcommunities. Particularly those that
OL,13,Fhave suffered deindustrialisation."
OL,15,FHe added that Burnham wants to build
OL,16,Fmore "social homes and create an
OL,17,Feconomy where business can thrive. I
OL,18,Fknow he wants this region to thrive
OL,19,Fjust as much as he does Greater
OL,20,FManchester."
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@Npn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FGetting the Midlands moving
OL,8,FOne thing we know about Andy Burnham
OL,9,Fis that he cares about transport.
OL,11,FIn his book, he uses the decision to
OL,12,Fscrap half of the HS2 project up to
OL,13,FManchester "without any consultation
OL,14,Fwith Northern Leaders" as the main
OL,15,Fexample of how Westminster is unequal
OL,16,Fand why power should be given to local
OL,17,Fleaders.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FHe also considers bringing
OL,7,FManchester's buses into public
OL,8,Fownership one of his biggest
OL,9,Fachievements as mayor of Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FNow, as PM we'll find out whether
OL,13,Fhe'll deliver on hints about reviving
OL,14,Fthe HS2 rail project past Birmingham.
OL,16,FThese suggestions have already been
OL,17,Fcriticised by the Newcastle Under Lyme
OL,18,Fborough council, as the line would
OL,19,Fpass through Madeley and Whitmore in
OL,20,FStaffordshire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FThe cost and the political fight to
OL,7,Fget work back underway would be
OL,8,Fsignificant, but it would also be a
OL,9,Fsymbol of his mission to correct the
OL,10,Fmistakes of the past.
OL,12,FAndy Burnham will also have the
OL,13,Funenviable task of looking for extra
OL,14,Fmoney to spend on defence.
OL,16,FKeir Starmer's government found a
OL,17,Fchunk of the cash by cancelling major
OL,18,Froad projects in the East Midlands.
OL,20,FThat was part of his #15 billion boost
OL,21,Fin defence spending.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784665115
OL,3,CWhat does PM Andy Burnham mean for the
OL,4,CMidlands?
OL,6,FThe #600 million A38 Derby junctions
OL,7,Fscheme and the A46 Newark Bypass were
OL,8,Fbig pieces of local infrastructure
OL,9,Fthat would have worked to address some
OL,10,Fimbalance of investment into the East
OL,11,FMidlands.
OL,13,FIn 2023`24, transport spending in the
OL,14,FEast Midlands was the lowest level of
OL,15,Fany part of the UK.
OL,17,FBringing the East Midlands up to
OL,18,Fparity with the rest of the country
OL,19,Fwill be a significant challenge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
